aim_castleground - Max people per team 20
 by Phaze (phaze@ezaya.fr)

Ten years ago, when i started CS, i really loved playground3. It was my favourite map !

I created this map with my child memories. This map looks like a playground3 but with my own touch ^^.

I would like to thanks Devi8 for his Bridge Prefabs. Very nice.

I hope you'll all enjoy playing on this map, have fun !


Phaze.
